title: Looking for a coach someone that can really teach me a lot about the jungle.

embed.description: Liquid Tempest / Silver 4 90LP / 14W 14L Win Ratio 50% / Jarvan IV - 8W 6L Win Ratio 57%, Tryndamere - 0W 4L Win Ratio 0%, Annie - 2W 1L Win Ratio 67%, Warwick - 1W 0L Win Ratio 100%, Lulu - 1W 0L Win Ratio 100%

body: Hi Looking for someone that can spend the time to teach me everything they know about the jungle and the key things that can help me improve and progress as i try my best to climb the rank ladder. I am currently silver 4 hit  gold last season. just looking for someone that can teach me.  :)

replies.body: Hey Message me on Discord: Thendoren#8303. I might have a proposition!
Hey im currently giving free lessons to people if u wanna catch up on Saturday or Sunday. I main top but started as a Jungler and its now my secondary. I maybe able to help u out just add me.

Watch people play Jungle, watch what they do in situations and how they think e.g you're invading the enemy buff top side and the enemy jungler isn't there obviously the jungler is bot and will probably either go for your blue buff or red buff or go to the buff you just took.
yeh i will do that aswell.

Just practice having someone teach you can really mess up your gameplay and you'll receive lots of criticism. Last time I was coached it made me worse because I had to change my habits and style lots.
